messages.messageBody:
Cris, Maddie and Quinn,

We can bring Barbie's.. I know it's not very creative but they are new and
sometimes popular. I'll bring a few of the two styles I have..

We also have new mini ponies with lil brushes. Prob 8-10 of those..
I know I have something else.. Slips my mind but I'll figure it out before
May.

Last MA convention we went on scholarship so I would be honored to add items
to assist others get there as we did..


See you there!

The Drew's ~ Family of 6 and counting the days....
UnschoolingMaine.com
